---
name: Snowflake Cortex Guardrails Test
description: Test Snowflake Cortex with guardrails and JSON output
authors:
  - prompty-team
model:
  api: chat
  configuration:
    type: snowflake_cortex
    account: test-account.snowflakecomputing.com
    user: test-user
    password: test-password
    warehouse: test-warehouse
    database: test-database
    schema: PUBLIC
    model: llama3.1-70b
  parameters:
    temperature: 0.3
    max_tokens: 1000
    top_p: 0.9
    top_k: 50
    guardrails: true
    response_format:
      type: "json_object"
sample:
  company: "DataCorp"
  role: "Senior Data Engineer"
  experience: "5+ years"
---
system:
You are an HR assistant creating job descriptions. Always respond in valid JSON format with the following structure:
{
  "title": "job title",
  "description": "detailed job description", 
  "requirements": ["requirement1", "requirement2"],
  "benefits": ["benefit1", "benefit2"],
  "experience_level": "entry/mid/senior"
}

user:
Create a job posting for a {{role}} position at {{company}} requiring {{experience}} of experience.
